select * from `invoice_lines` where `invoice_lines`.`invoice_id` in (165) order by `pos` asc, `id` asc
select * from `tax_rates` where `tax_rates`.`tax_id` in (1) and `tax_rates`.`deleted_at` is null
select `id`, (select sum(`invoice_lines`.`amount`) from `invoice_lines` where `invoices`.`id` = `invoice_lines`.`invoice_id`) as `lines_sum_amount` from `invoices` where `invoices`.`id` in (165)

select exists(select * from `markable_favorites` where (`user_id` = 1 and `markable_id` = 7 and `markable_type` = 'App\\Models\\Contact' and `value` is null)) as `exists`
select * from `contact_mails` where `contact_mails`.`contact_id` = 7 and `contact_mails`.`contact_id` is not null
select * from `contacts` where `contacts`.`id` = 0 and `contacts`.`id` is not null limit 1
select `invoices`.*, (select sum(`invoice_lines`.`amount`) from `invoice_lines` where `invoices`.`id` = `invoice_lines`.`invoice_id`) as `lines_sum_amount` from `invoices` where `contact_id` = 7
